Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.16,00:00:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever heard of Coil?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:01.19,00:00:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me break it down real quick.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:02.56,00:00:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Coil stands for Collaborative Online International Learning and it's a
Dialogue: 0,00:00:06.12,00:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,game changer in global education.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:08.00,00:00:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine students from universities in different countries joining forces on
Dialogue: 0,00:00:11.27,00:00:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,shared courses.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:12.16,00:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some basic online class.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:13.91,00:00:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fully interactive with professors co teaching and guiding real
Dialogue: 0,00:00:17.28,00:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:18.80,00:00:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic of Coil is in the connections.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:21.28,00:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Students aren't just learning, they're building trust, solving problems, comparing
Dialogue: 0,00:00:25.55,00:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,perspectives and and crafting projects together.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:27.85,00:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about multicultural collaboration with a blend of synchronous
Dialogue: 0,00:00:31.42,00:00:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sessions like live video calls and asynchronous work so everyone
Dialogue: 0,00:00:35.42,00:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,stays on track globally.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:37.53,00:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Coil isn't just another distance learning or social media
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.85,00:00:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,group.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:41.38,00:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's structured, moderated and project driven.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.17,00:00:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's icebreakers, comparative discussions or presenting final work, every
Dialogue: 0,00:00:48.53,00:00:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,step is planned for meaningful engagement.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.03,00:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's next?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.14,00:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get involved.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:54.03,00:00:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Introduce yourself on Padlet, join the sessions and experience firsthand
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.67,00:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,how tech and global teamwork are reshaping education.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:01.14,00:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to connect across continents?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.75,00:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
